data.description: Don't miss out!! Come see this nicely updated 5 bedroom 3 bath home with a separate office. Situated on a fully fenced in corner lot this home offers a large eat in kitchen with all new stainless steel appliances included. It also has a large living room, open and great for entertaining. There are 3 bedrooms downstairs and 2 more upstairs and an office, & new life proof flooring. It also offers an above ground pool, a nice covered patio. New roof 2019.
